</video>
<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">"I Just Don't Feel Safe"</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
During a drive on &quot;Canada's Worst Driver Ever,&quot; Kevin is told that his drive is done if he commits another ticketable offense. He proceeds to almost turn left against a red light and then when it does turn, it's into oncoming traffic. Host Andrew is forced to end the drive, telling Kevin that he just doesn't feel safe driving with him. Kevin very well could be Canada's Worst Driver... Ever.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="c79xjn">
<input type="hidden" name="is_logged_in" value="0">
